## Gotchas
WRONG: storing JWT in localStorage
RIGHT: store in httpOnly cookie with Secure + SameSite flags
WHY: localStorage is accessible via XSS. httpOnly cookies are not readable by JavaScript.

WRONG: long-lived access tokens (24h+)
RIGHT: short access token (15min) + refresh token rotation
WHY: Long-lived tokens can't be revoked. Short + refresh allows rotation and revocation.

[Add more WRONG/RIGHT/WHY blocks as you discover them.]

